overview: In 'Club 18-23', Alex Summers wants to join an exclusive club just for members between the ages of 18 and 23. Several friends are already members and they tell their hot experiences. First, there's an orgy between Marco Antonio, Cory Adams, Rod Barry and Lucas James, then Tony Cummings and Richie Fine get down together. Next, Alex Summers bottoms for Shane Thomas, finally, Jordan Austin and Brad Hunter get it up together!
title: Club 18-23
